<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>BR Buyback</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Premium landing page for BR Buyback with quote instructions, purchase procedure and click-to-text/call actions." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#f6f3ee;
      --surface:#fbfaf7;
      --surface-2:#f1ede6;
      --surface-3:#ece7df;
      --text:#171512;
      --muted:#67625b;
      --line:#d9d1c5;
      --primary:#0c655b;
      --primary-hover:#084a43;
      --gold:#b88b22;
      --gold-soft:#eee0bc;
      --success:#2f6d2f;
      --shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(29,26,20,.10);
      --radius:24px;
      --max:1160px;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(184,139,34,.12), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(12,101,91,.10), transparent 22%),
        var(--bg);
      line-height:1.58;
    }
    a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}
    .wrap{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;padding:20px}
    .topbar{
      display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:14px;
      padding:8px 0 18px;
    }
    .brand{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
      min-width:0;
    }
    .mark{
      width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:16px;
      background:linear-gradient(145deg,#131313,#2b2b2b);
      position:relative;box-shadow:var(--shadow);flex:0 0 auto;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .mark:before{
      content:'';position:absolute;inset:8px;border-radius:12px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,.10),rgba(255,255,255,.02));
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
    .mark svg{position:absolute;inset:0;margin:auto;width:30px;height:30px;color:#fff}
    .brand-copy strong{display:block;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:-.03em}
    .brand-copy span{display:block;font-size:.86rem;color:var(--muted)}
    .top-actions{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .ghost{
      min-height:44px;padding:11px 15px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:600
    }
    .hero{
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:22px;align-items:stretch;padding:8px 0 20px;
    }
    .hero-main,.hero-side,.panel{background:rgba(251,250,247,.84);border:1px solid rgba(217,209,197,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
    .hero-main{
      border-radius:32px;padding:34px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    }
    .hero-main:after{
      content:'';position:absolute;right:-90px;top:-70px;width:240px;height:240px;border-radius:999px;
      background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(184,139,34,.16), transparent 62%);
    }
    .eyebrow{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
      padding:10px 14px;border-radius:999px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--line);font-size:.88rem;font-weight:700;
    }
    .eyebrow i{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--gold));display:inline-block}
    h1{
      font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;
      font-size:clamp(2.7rem,6vw,5.8rem);
      line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.05em;margin:18px 0 18px;max-width:11ch;font-weight:400;
    }
    .hero p{
      color:var(--muted);font-size:1.03rem;max-width:62ch;margin:0 0 24px;
    }
    .cta-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px}
    .btn{
      min-height:50px;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;
      transition:.18s ease;
    }
    .btn-primary{background:var(--primary);color:#fff}
    .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--primary-hover);transform:translateY(-1px)}
    .btn-secondary{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line)}
    .meta{
      display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem
    }
    .hero-side{
      border-radius:32px;padding:24px;display:grid;gap:14px;
    }
    .quote-card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#151515,#252525);color:#fff;border-radius:26px;padding:20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    }
    .quote-card:after{
      content:'';position:absolute;inset:auto -60px -60px auto;width:170px;height:170px;border-radius:999px;background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(184,139,34,.35), transparent 60%);
    }
    .quote-card small{display:block;color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);margin-bottom:8px}
    .quote-card h2{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:1.25rem;letter-spacing:-.03em}
    .quote-list{display:grid;gap:10px;margin-top:14px}
    .quote-item{padding:12px 13px;border-radius:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);font-size:.94rem}
    .mini-note{padding:16px;border-radius:18px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--line);font-size:.94rem;color:var(--muted)}
    .section-grid{
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-top:20px;
    }
    .panel{border-radius:28px;padding:26px}
    .panel h3{margin:0 0 14px;font-size:1.24rem;letter-spacing:-.03em}
    .stack{display:grid;gap:12px}
    .stack .box{
      padding:15px 16px;border-radius:18px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--line)
    }
    .stack .box strong{display:block;margin-bottom:4px}
    .steps{display:grid;gap:12px}
    .step{display:grid;grid-template-columns:44px 1fr;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;padding:14px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;background:#fff}
    .num{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:999px;background:var(--text);color:#fff;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800}
    .accept{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:12px}
    .chip{padding:10px 13px;border-radius:999px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--line);font-size:.9rem}
    .highlight{
      margin-top:16px;padding:16px 18px;border-radius:18px;background:#fff7e4;border:1px solid #e9d59e
    }
    .bottom-cta{
      margin:22px 0 36px;padding:24px;border-radius:28px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#102421,#17312d);color:#fff;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:18px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;box-shadow:var(--shadow)
    }
    .bottom-cta p{margin:0;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);max-width:50ch}
    .footer{padding:4px 0 40px;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem}
    @media (max-width: 900px){
      .hero,.section-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      h1{max-width:none}
      .topbar{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px){
      .hero-main,.hero-side,.panel,.bottom-cta{padding:20px}
      .mark{width:46px;height:46px}
      .btn,.ghost{width:100%}
      .top-actions,.cta-row{width:100%}
      .top-actions > *, .cta-row > * {flex:1 1 100%}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="mark" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M15 13H27.5C32.2 13 35 15.5 35 19.4C35 22.3 33.2 24.2 30.4 24.8C33.8 25.3 36 27.6 36 31.1C36 35.5 32.7 38 27.4 38H15V13Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M23 24H28.3C31 24 32.6 22.9 32.6 20.4C32.6 18 31 16.9 28.3 16.9H23V24Z" fill="currentColor"/>
            <path d="M23 34.1H28.7C31.8 34.1 33.3 32.7 33.3 30.1C33.3 27.4 31.6 26.2 28.6 26.2H23V34.1Z" fill="currentColor"/>
            <path d="M13 13V38" stroke="url(#g)" stroke-width="3.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="g" x1="13" y1="13" x2="13" y2="38" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                <stop stop-color="#C59A2A"/>
                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#0E6A60"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-copy">
          <strong>BR Buyback</strong>
          <span>Apple device buyer</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="top-actions">
        <a class="ghost" href="sms:+19546619570?body=Hi Sergio, I want a quote for my Apple device. Model:%20 Storage:%20 Condition:%20 Battery:%20 Any defects:%20">Text Sergio</a>
        <a class="ghost" href="tel:+19546619570">Call 954-661-9570</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-main">
        <div class="eyebrow"><i></i> Instant cash for Apple devices</div>
        <h1>Simple quote. Clear process. Fast payment.</h1>
        <p>This page tells you exactly what to send for a quote and how the purchase works. No vague back and forth. Just the key details needed to evaluate your Apple device correctly.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="sms:+19546619570?body=Hi Sergio, I want a quote for my Apple device. Model:%20 Storage:%20 Condition:%20 Battery:%20 Any defects:%20">Text for instant quote</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="tel:+19546619570">Call now</a>
        </div>
        <div class="meta">
          <span>Sergio Queiroz</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>Miami area</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>Used, damaged and selected Apple devices</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-side">
        <div class="quote-card">
          <small>What determines the quote</small>
          <h2>Every offer is based on actual device details.</h2>
          <div class="quote-list">
            <div class="quote-item">Model and generation</div>
            <div class="quote-item">Storage capacity</div>
            <div class="quote-item">Cosmetic condition</div>
            <div class="quote-item">Battery or power status</div>
            <div class="quote-item">Functional issues or defects</div>
            <div class="quote-item">Lock status and eligibility</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-note"><strong>Accepted categories:</strong> iPhone, Mac, iPad, Apple Watch and selected accessories depending on condition and resale value.</div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="section-grid">
      <article class="panel">
        <h3>How to send a good quote request</h3>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="box"><strong>Model</strong> Example: iPhone 13 Pro, MacBook Air M1, iPad Air 5.</div>
          <div class="box"><strong>Storage</strong> Example: 128GB, 256GB, 512GB or 1TB.</div>
          <div class="box"><strong>Cosmetic condition</strong> Say if it is clean, scratched, dented, cracked or heavily worn.</div>
          <div class="box"><strong>Battery or power</strong> For iPhone, include battery health if possible. For Mac, mention battery condition if known.</div>
          <div class="box"><strong>Functional condition</strong> Mention any issue with screen, Face ID, camera, charging, buttons, speakers, keyboard or trackpad.</div>
          <div class="box"><strong>Lock status</strong> The device must not be iCloud locked and must not be reported stolen.</div>
          <div class="box"><strong>Photos</strong> Send clear photos of front, back, sides and any visible damage.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight"><strong>Recommended text:</strong><br>Hi Sergio, I have an iPhone 13 128GB. Good condition, 86% battery health, everything works, no iCloud lock. Small scratches on frame. I can send photos now.</div>
      </article>

      <article class="panel">
        <h3>How the purchase and payment work</h3>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><div><strong>You send the device details.</strong><br>Model, storage, condition and a few photos are enough to start.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><div><strong>You receive a quote.</strong><br>The amount is based on current buyback value and the actual condition described.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="num">3</div><div><strong>The device is checked in person.</strong><br>The final amount depends on the device matching the description and photos.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="num">4</div><div><strong>Payment is made immediately after verification.</strong><br>If everything checks out, the purchase is completed on the spot.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accept">
          <span class="chip">iPhone</span>
          <span class="chip">Mac</span>
          <span class="chip">iPad</span>
          <span class="chip">Apple Watch</span>
          <span class="chip">AirPods</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight"><strong>Important:</strong> Devices must be fully yours to sell, not financed with unpaid installments, not blacklisted and not iCloud locked. A valid ID may be requested for higher-value transactions.</div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="bottom-cta">
      <div>
        <strong style="display:block;font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:6px;letter-spacing:-.03em;">Ready to get your quote?</strong>
        <p>Send the model, storage, condition and a few photos. That is the fastest way to get a serious number back.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-row" style="margin:0;">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="sms:+19546619570?body=Hi Sergio, I want a quote for my Apple device. Model:%20 Storage:%20 Condition:%20 Battery:%20 Any defects:%20">Text now</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" style="background:#fff;color:#111;" href="tel:+19546619570">Call Sergio</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">BR Buyback · Sergio Queiroz · 954-661-9570</footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
